All carrier and essential oils used are 100% natural and therapeutic grade, intended for use on the skin. A spiced, floral and fresh blend has been formulated in each of our potions to implement the intent of what each of these Potion oils have to offer.

Apply anywhere on the skin whilst you speak the intent of the potion or your chosen mantra, chant or affirmation to yourself. Can be used to anoint your wallet, purse, door frames, candles, during ritual, and in your daily skincare routine!
